#### img appearance

#### imgsets

```python
imgsets(
    img,
    sets=None,
    show=True,
    show_axis=False,
    size=None,
    dpi=100,
    figsize=None,
    auto=False,
    filter_kws=None,
)
```

```python
img = imgsets(
    fpath,
    sets={"rota": -5, "sharp": 10},
    dpi=200,
    # show_axis=True,
)
figsave(dir_save, "test1_sharp.pdf")


img2 = imgsets(
    fpath,
    sets={"rota": -5, "crop": [100, 100, 300, 400], "sharp": 10},
    dpi=200,
    filter_kws={
        "sharpen": 10,
    },
    # show_axis=True,
)
figsave(dir_save, "test2_crop.pdf")
```

